  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/digitalcamera/\" rel=\"tag\">数码相机</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/robots/\" rel=\"tag\">智能机器</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/02/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-and-nx-30\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/5e3d86a6eccf56dfec2c92ad01ddaeeb/samsung-nx30-and-galaxy-camera-2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<br />\nSamsung 选择在 CES 之前尽早更新自己的相机系列，在今天分别发表了他们最新一代的智慧型相机 Galaxy Camera 2 与 NX30，两者都跟上了最新以 NFC 近场通讯为基础的\"Tag &amp; Go\"分享功能。藉此功能将可直接将两部相机靠近感应，即可直接快速地配对并传输照片。Samsung 亦升级了他们在行动装置上的专属 App 以跟上此功能。跳转后观看详细的规格介绍。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/\">Samsung Galaxy Camera 2</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/6414999/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc02690-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/6415000/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc02691-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/6415001/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc02693-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/6415002/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc02694-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-camera-2-0/6415003/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc02695-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-galaxy-nx-30/\">Samsung Galaxy NX 30</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-ga